API:

In weather_api.py and app.py find this line no.3 API_KEY = "" and line no.14 PENWEATHER_KEY = ""

Now go to " https://openweathermap.org/api " and create api key and put it.

Run for first time.

In terminal:

Step 1:
py -3.11 -m venv venv

Step 2:
venv\Scripts\activate

Step 3:
pip install -r requirements.txt

Step 4:
py app.py


For regular run adter first time run:

Step 1:
py -3.11 -m venv venv

Step 2:
venv\Scripts\activate

Step 3:
py app.py
